        "created_at": "2024-12-26T06:02:02.188Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When the user does not allow the contact’s access, the New Call Screen is quite Empty. It only shows an <code>Invite to Signal</code> and a Search Bar(which doesn’t logically make sense). We should have the ‘Allow Contacts’ card in the New Call screen like in the New Chat Screen. This way the screen won’t look empty and will maintain consistency without much effort. Some changes in the ContactSelectionListFragment and NewCallActivity can easily do this.</p>",
