        "created_at": "2024-12-26T06:05:23.783Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The search makes sense, because you can have Signal connections (people you have previously chatted with) without giving access to your phone’s contacts.</p>\n<p>The part that doesn’t make sense is that the new call screen doesn’t have the “Find by username” and “Find by phone number” options that the new message screen does. Seems like that may have been overlooked.</p>",
