        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/sagar0-0/{size}/50022_2.png",
        "created_at": "2024-12-26T06:20:54.120Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for the clarification on the Search feature.</p>\n<p>Yes, “Find by username” and “Find by Number” should also be there. However, I am unsure if we can directly call or video call the users from this screen. Maybe, it’s not a good privacy practice and that’s why these are not there?</p>\n<p>Also, What are your views on the “Allow contacts” cards, that should be there too?</p>\n<p>These can be easily configured with ContactSelectionListFragment, I am preety familiar with the codebase now.</p>",
